{"id":186890,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011106/","date":"2011-10-07T19:30:44Z","modified":"2011-10-07T19:30:44Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/10/6","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><span> </span><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21531524\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">辛亥革命百年：从孙到毛到现在</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国当局对纪念辛亥革命倍加小心，因为它不想让人们把焦点放在反抗恶势力政府和争取民主上面。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/07/world/asia/12-punished-for-shanghai-subway-crash.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上海地铁事故，</span>12<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人因玩忽职守而被处罚</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——十号线总调度员等人受到开除和降职等不同处分。政府称信号故障也是事故原因之一。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业内幕》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/rebalancing-chinese-economy-that-almost-impossible-math-2011-10\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">从数学角度看，中国的经济转型几乎不可能做到</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——没人怀疑中国想要转型为消费主导的经济，但是从上个五年计划开始他们就要转，到现在情况越来越差。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">欧亚评论：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eurasiareview.com/01032011-china-pla%E2%80%99s-ascendancy-in-propaganda-warfare/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">解放军在宣传战中崛起</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中共执政的手段之一就是依靠宣传。近年来，解放军也被要求加强打赢媒体战、心理战和法律战的训练。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20111006/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_credit_crunch\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国总理呼吁帮助负债企业</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据当地官员介绍，温州</span></span><span><span>36</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万中小企业中，有</span></span><span><span>1/5</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">因资金短缺而停业。温家宝考察温州后表示要提供资金支持</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业内幕》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/china-underground-banking-system-2011-10?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+businessinsider+%28Business+Insider%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的地下银行系统是怎么回事，以及为什么你应该对它感到害怕</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/10/06/netizens-respond-to-steve-jobss-death/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国网民对乔布斯去世发表看法</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——许多网民在微博上表示对乔布斯的悼念和惋惜，也有人开玩笑说他是被</span></span><span><span>iphone4s</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">气死的。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/10/china-macau-and-steve-jobs.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国来信：中国、澳门和乔布斯</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——乔布斯在中国人心目中占据了一个特殊的位置：他是一位创新者，同时具有超越国界的品味。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/oct/06/china-carbon-emission-forecasts-economy\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">数据表明中国将超出碳排放预测量</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——最新研究表明中国发展速度超过预期，而且无力摆脱碳排放密集的行业，因此将超过原来预计的排放量。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国节奏博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thechinabeat.org/?p=3854\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对“汉文化圈”的不同看法</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——本文对《福布斯》专栏作家提出的汉文化圈经济现象提出异议，认为它并非铁板一块，不应笼统地被圈在一起。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/06/world/middleeast/with-united-nations-veto-russia-and-china-help-syria.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中俄在利比亚问题上少见地双双投反对票，是为了保护自己的朋友</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中俄不想看到曾是社会主义阵营一员的叙利亚被阿拉伯之春的浪潮吞没</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/06/us-usa-china-idUSN1E7950FF20111006?feedType=RSS&#038;feedName=Yuan&#038;virtualBrandChannel=11721&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+reuters%2FUSyuanNews+%28News+%2F+US+%2F+YUAN+GCA%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">奥巴马批评中国的贸易政策</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然他并未表态支持参议院关于中国汇率的惩罚议案，但他指责中国压低汇率钻国际贸易的空子。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/china-officials-yelping-dogs-us-senator-185201336.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国参议员称中国官员像叫唤的狗</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“如果你向一群狗扔块石头，叫唤的那只就是被你砸中的</span></span><span><span>…</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">当然中国会叫唤，因为他们不喜欢这个议案。”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/2011/10/03/forget-greece-it-s-china/5pmt\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">忘掉希腊吧，中国更危险</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——拥有</span></span><span><span>13</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿人口的中国一旦经济停滞，其后果远比希腊的危机更严重。而近来中国传来的数据不容乐观</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-10-06/china-air-travel-trails-capacity-growth-in-golden-week-holiday.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国黄金周，飞机乘客人数增幅不到运量增幅的一半</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——制造业和房地产的降温使消费者花钱更谨慎。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/10/06/china-isnt-safe/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国不安全？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——外国人在中国一般都会感到很安全，但当地中国人却不太同意。到处可见的防盗提示和防盗门似乎证明了这一点。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21531525\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">最后的满族人</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——一百年前，满语是一个大国的国语，而如今会说它的寥寥无几。东北一位</span></span><span><span>86</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的老太太据说是最后两位能说流利满语的人之一。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-7927174703151190003?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[8840]}